description: Is it a frightfully hot summer day? Have no fear! SnoBites Shaved Ice is here to save the day! Now you can beat the heat with a refreshingly sweet frozen treat. This family-owned truck features the top Tropical Sno™ flavors (Lemon, Banana, Strawberry, Cotton Candy (etc..), as well as their own creative concoctions, and toppings (banana, vanilla, coconut cream). Lucky Las Vegans, know that when it comes to nicely shaved ice, there’s no bites like SnoBites.
name: SnoBites Shaved Ice
